snippet.title: Exverse Tournament Trailer
snippet.description: Dive into the year 2085 with Exverse, a gripping FPS that merges intense shooter gameplay with innovative Web3 mechanics. After a cataclysmic event rendered Earth a wasteland, humanity clings to survival in space. As the planet's flora unleashed a deadly toxin, the race to save or abandon Earth divides humanity.
